dBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n會出既無論點封都係會行路照出<br />\n唔出既講極都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"病到仆街點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0811da4140383fe473cdc473eba98890501da0","tid":1609792,"uid":256261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"[US immigration alert]<br />\n<br />\n說明多元化移民簽證，又稱抽籤移民簽證或綠卡抽獎，是美國政府每年基於《移民與國籍法》第203條的規定為特定國家所舉辦的活動，吸引合資格申請人移民美國，在當地生活和工作，每年名額為50,000人。 <br />\n<br />\n資格：<br />\n1. 是香港人<br />\n2. 已高中畢業 （完成12年教育）或 已有2年工作經驗<br />\n<br />\nThe US Department of State annually administers the statutorily-mandated Diversity Immigrant Visa Program. For Fiscal Year 2021, 55,000 Diversity Visas (DVs) will be available. <br />\n<br />\nThere is NO COST to register for the DV program. <br />\n<br />\nFor DV-2021, mainland Chinese are not eligible to apply, because more than 50,000 PRC citizens immigrated to the United States in the previous five years. Persons born in HONG KONG SAR are eligible.<br />\n<br />\nApplicants must submit entries for the DV-2021 program electronically at <a href=\"http://dvlottery.state.gov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdvlottery.state.gov&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=e22bd968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">dvlottery.state.gov</a> between noon, Eastern Daylight Time (EDT) (GMT-4), Wednesday, October 2, 2019, and noon, Eastern Standard Time (EST) (GMT-5), Tuesday, November 5, 2019.<br />\n<br />\n詳情請參閱以下文件<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.state.gov/content/dam/visas/Diversity-Visa/DV-Instructions-Translations/DV-2021-Instructions-Translations/DV-2021-Instructions-English.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fvisas%2FDiversity-Visa%2FDV-Instructions-Translations%2FDV-2021-Instructions-Translations%2FDV-2021-Instructions-English.pdf&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=c41da419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://travel.state.gov/content/dam/visas/Diversity-Visa/DV-Instructions-Translations/DV-2021-Instructions-Translations/DV-2021-Instructions-English.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"f8b8a5b9cbc9408211c4df30afae3af4787d3232","tid":1609792,"uid":124636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"港島好撚多喎，比9.29嗰次已經多左好多，至少30萬"},{"pid":"ccbf5544e783084e25bd4eecc6dfd079ddc6afa6","tid":1609792,"uid":268929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"點會唔夠人啊？區區都好多人。"}]}